\lang1033\b\f1\fs16 White to play\lang1042\b0\f0\fs18
\lang1033\f1\fs16 Again, we have a White stone somewhere in the inside of Black's eye space and we need to figure out how to best use it to kill Black.

Where is the vital point?

\lang1042\f0\fs18
])
(;AW[pp][qp][rp][sp][mq][nq][oq][mr][ms][ns][ss]AB[pq][qq][rq][sq][nr][or][rr][ps]
